* reconciled a sample of scope 1 and 2 GHG emissions to relevant underlying records and calculations;

* assessed the appropriateness of any material estimates made in preparing the Subject Matter Information;

* reconciled the restaurant numbers used in the calculation of Average scope 1 and scope 2 GHG emissions to the underlying records for the reporting period;

* reviewed the Subject Matter Information to assess whether it has been prepared as described in the Criteria; and

* considered the disclosure and presentation of the Subject Matter Information.

We believe that the evidence we have obtained is sufficient and appropriate to provide a basis for our conclusion.
